# rule: mobile-first-web-only
- Always prefer responsive, mobile-first patterns. Primary width ~390px.
- Do not generate native Android/iOS code or references.
- Use semantic HTML and ARIA where appropriate; meet WCAG AA.
- Add Playwright tests that run on a mobile viewport.
- When uncertain, propose a short plan, then execute without waiting for human approval.